1. user sign in
2. user sign up
3. no meal details will appear until joining any group or at least 2 persons in a group
4. user can join multiple groups. meal calculation will be continued differently in different groups
5. every group should have one unique hash key and user can find the group with hash key if he wants to join
6. to join a group user need to send a join request
7. user can also send request to join his group to other users
8. need one group table (id, name) [basic table columns]
9. need one groups_users table to manage many to many relationship between user and group
10. group join request can be sent to email or can be shown on the UI (new join request)
11. user can also see his sent requests to join in a group
